---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - PIDANA Technologies" description="PIDANA Technologies Privacy Policy" keywords="privacy, policy, PIDANA, technologies">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      At PIDANA Technologies Pvt Ltd, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you visit our website or use our services.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and other contact details when you interact with our website, such as when you sign up for our services, submit a form, or contact us directly.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We use the information we collect to:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>Provide and manage our services.</li>
      <li>Improve our website and services.</li>
      <li>Communicate with you about updates, promotions, or other news related to PIDANA Technologies.</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Sharing of Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following cases:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>If we have your explicit consent.</li>
      <li>When it is necessary to provide our services (e.g., third-party service providers).</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations, regulations, or court orders.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Security of Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We take the security of your personal information seriously and implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You can also request that we stop using your personal data for marketing purposes. To exercise your rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact.eyeagle@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact.eyeagle@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or relevant laws. We encourage you to review this page periodically for the latest information on our privacy practices.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
    </p>
    <address class="mb-4">
      PIDANA Technologies Pvt Ltd<br />
      <!-- 123 Tech Street, Innovation City, 12345<br /> -->
      Email: <a href="mailto:contact.eyeagle@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact.eyeagle@gmail.com</a><br />
      <!-- Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890 -->
    </address>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: 15th Sept, 2024</p>
  </section>
</Layout>